title: A good Mundo jungler maxes what first?
body: Cz I feel like maxing Q first could be wrong.

replies.body: When Mundo was a strong jungler S3 it was W max, but camps have more HP on one big target now.  E max was the transition, because you could run attack speed Marks and Quints and kill stuff really quick.  Now?  I dunno.  Probably Q, because it kills the big monsters pretty quick and is what you want maxed for team fights.
i put 2 in w, then max q
Q gives you way more jungle clear speed than W and E
